name: Cube Masters (EnricoGameDev)
description:
Cube Masters is a game where you press A & D to go Left & Right. In later levels, you can press Space to Jump on the darker areas.

This game was heavily inspired by Brackeys, he made a tutorial series where he made this game. But I improved on it. So a huge shoutout to Brackeys for the HUGE Help and inspiration!

My Youtube Channel!
